personal_info.summary: Experienced full-stack web developer with a strong background in business administration. Proficient in Node.js, JavaScript, TypeScript, React, Redux, Sequelize, Express, PostgreSQL, Prisma, and MongoDB. Skilled in agile methodologies, data structures, algorithms, GIT, and CSS frameworks like Tailwind. Effective communicator and collaborative team player. Detail-oriented with a knack for identifying errors. Thrives in fast-paced work environments. Passionate about career opportunities in the IT sector.
